title: Graphics::EnumerateMetafile(IN const Metafile,IN const PointF,IN INT,IN const RectF &,IN Unit,IN EnumerateMetafileProc,IN VOID,IN const ImageAttributes) (gdiplusgraphics.h)
description: The Graphics::EnumerateMetafile method calls an application-defined callback function for each record in a specified metafile. You can use this method to display a metafile by calling PlayRecord in the callback function. (overload 12/12)
